      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, test sample characterization must confirm fluid properties within ±10% of nominal blood-analog values.",
      "rationale": "Blood-analog fluid (glycerin-water) characterized at 37°C prior to testing. Formal statistical sample size analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
