      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, dimensional similarity between validation and COU conditions must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds number and flow coefficient matching between validation bench conditions and COU operating envelope documented. Formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2."
